{
  "contextFiles": [
    "README.md",
    "docs/**/*.md",
    "docs/adr/*.md",
    "openapi.yaml"
  ],
  "fileIncludePatterns": [
    "apps/frontend/**/*.tsx",
    "packages/ui/**/*.tsx",
    "apps/api/**/*.ts",
    "packages/hooks/**/*.ts",
    "infra/**/*.{ts,tf,yml}",
    "prisma/schema.prisma"
  ],
  "autoImports": [
    {
      "module": "react",
      "symbols": [
        "useState",
        "useEffect",
        "FC",
        "ReactNode"
      ]
    },
    {
      "module": "@prisma/client",
      "symbols": [
        "PrismaClient"
      ]
    },
    {
      "module": "zod",
      "symbols": [
        "z",
        "ZodSchema"
      ]
    },
    {
      "module": "tailwind-merge",
      "symbols": [
        "twMerge"
      ]
    },
    {
      "module": "@opentelemetry/sdk-node",
      "symbols": [
        "NodeSDK"
      ]
    }
  ],
  "generationHints": [
    "Usa hooks y functional components en React",
    "Cuando detectes un modelo Prisma, genera validaciones Zod",
    "Prefiere CSS-in-JS con className y tailwind-merge",
    "Al generar nuevos endpoints, incluye validaci√≥n de body con Zod",
    "En infra-as-code, usa AWS CDK y patrones de Stack/Construct"
  ],
  "completion": {
    "style": [
      "className",
      "tw",
      "cn"
    ],
    "maxSuggestions": 5,
    "includeSnippets": true
  }
}